nsd for Debian
--------------

- I have moved /etc/nsd/nsdc.conf to /etc/default/nsdc
- Zone file is rebuild automaticaly on nsd startup.
- I have copied named-xfer binary from bind 8.4.4 package and renamed
  it to nsd-xfer along with man page.

